{"tid":2101094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"721你哋諗住點㗎？","createTime":"2020-07-09T13:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T16:04:57.000Z","uid":99725,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"644d0232d6afbc449116e7a3a672e9bc271ce116","tid":2101094,"uid":99725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T13:57:39.000Z","msg":"一年前，元朗地鐵站發生嘅恐怖襲擊同埋警黑勾結可以話係震驚全港。<br />\n我好記得當晚連登有一個po話727要入元朗燒村，如果嗰個po我冇記錯都有幾千正評，可見當時我哋係有幾憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n而721事件亦都係成為我哋口中嘅核彈之一。<br />\n<br />\n事隔一年，我想知道香港人仲會唔會好似上年咁，無視反對通知書咁入元朗行街。"},{"pid":"5da4a67c82bcebe297e8b203acfc54bfd58f7578","tid":2101094,"uid":99725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T13:58:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"131e99497538ed0ce4153ed0ae2e0903ea6eed4f","tid":2101094,"uid":275613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T13:59:15.000Z","msg":"輸咗"},{"pid":"8061bdfaa771ffe3fd23bee6bfaa25ca995a9bf1","tid":2101094,"uid":99725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T13:59:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8391cbc3b67b034441b84cfd2eb6dcf31bbbb6df","tid":2101094,"uid":99725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:00:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d63ae1445bd26ff4b03211247380dc9241ede1cd","tid":2101094,"uid":99725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dccc385e86c87c98674bfd2265dd9e147b5b3509","tid":2101094,"uid":262480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"已經攞左假<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45024eec031251724c6c4c31425658b5afcea7df","tid":2101094,"uid":99725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:03:17.000Z","msg":"我想知大家點諗"},{"pid":"cdfc981d73d76e8042241bf9620fb9cfea6d2b47","tid":2101094,"uid":171302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"rep